@node Main "Lightit - Documentation"

                             'Lightit' 1.11

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Lightit' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where the goal is to switch on
all the light bulbs on an hexagonal shaped board. When you complete
a game level, the game displays a new level, where more lights are
turned on or off...

  The game offers two difficulty levels: @{" Easy " link play} or @{" Harder " link play}.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
